Fir to tum hall 2 ke hi ho gaye the...wo agra ki trip me sabko sambhalne se lekar har waqt kisi na kisi ko apna kandha deta rehta tha tu bro...wo udhari jo birthday treat s start hoti thi apan ki wo tere se kabhi khatam nahi hoti thi aur...next yaer hi dena yaad aata thağŸ˜. text: Hey CHM lab partner, although I was never your lab partner... par esc aur chm common courses the apne...I still remember ki kya nickname dia tha maine tumhe ğŸ˜...first year me cycling pe jana aur vampire diaries ke tumhre cliche jokes(PJ bhi bol sakte hai)...I remember them all. Humari baatein baad me kam ho gayi thi....so writing here to let you know ki memories hai tere sath bhi and I wish aur bhi hoti...terms that I learnt from you- TKLD, DKDğŸ¤¢...aise hi PJ marte rehnaâœŒï¸ğŸ¤

text:
Roomie se start kare ya apni family tree ke chutiyap se...bapu apna "tatti" tha aur uski wajah se sath me ragging hue thi apni mess me...first year ka m moments to epic the , wo Nagle ke room ke bahar kaali ch**t chilane se lekar C bot ke saare darwaze band karne tak...bahut kaand kie hai. C/231 me pehli baar apan me daru pee thi...aur fir waha se apne nashedi kahaniya shuru hui thi...2nd year me roomie mai kaise bana ye to pata hi hai ğŸ˜‚...par mai bahut khush hu. Raat me endless bitching se lekar wo 0101 ka chutiyapa mai zindagi bhar nahi bhulunga.

Sabse zada maze apan ne hi liye hai...wo PUBG ka pagalpan...aur momo wale ki dukaan jana sab apne ko exams me hi yaad aata tha...I am glad ki hum log monoply khelte the aur fir uske baad ki ladaiyan jab mai pata nahi kaise jeet jata tha aur parv aur mai tumhe chidate the... memories agar likhne baitha to shayad khatam na ho....par ek baat ka regret rahega humesha ki humari Bhutan ki trip nahi ho sakiğŸ˜...humesha aise hi bane rehna aur kismat teri meri hi jaise chudi hui hai. Tere bimar hone par 2nd year me gir jaane par breakfast lane se...aur mere hath katne par hospital le jaane tak... always there for each other. Bhale hi apni kafi baat na ho par jab milenge tab khub maze karenge...aur apni party wagrh to bachi hai...this time don't do "zero one zero one"â¤ï¸
author: Utkarsh  Sonkar

text: Kab tu hall 2 ka launda bann gaya pata hi nahi chala...poori summer me mere room par rehta tha aur student lounge par bakchodiya....sabse best memory agra ki hai apni ,jab vedanth bola chaggi ko chadhi hai wo daru nahi laa payega... fir jo rum(issi rum ki bottle pe thaga tha tumko theke wale ne) ki bottle se usko chadhi aur waha par jo machaya...sabse important jo tha wo thi udhari jo meri tere se khtm hi nahi hua karti thi...bhai maze to bohot kiye hai aur kabhi nahi socha tha kab dost se bhai ban jaega tu.... right from Hisar ğŸ˜bahut bakchod launde mile hai.... hopefully aage bhi milte rahenge aur party karte rahenge. Most importantly aise hi bane rehna never change ğŸ¤
author: Utkarsh  Sonkar

text: Tum wo launde ho jisne pehli baar cigarette fookna sikhaya....first year ki bakchodi se lekar kar wo swaroop nagar me theke ke bahar beer pee ke rasta bhulna restaurant tak ka....aur A top ki wing se niche bed ka plywood fek dena...sab yaad rahega through up and downs sab bakchodiya sath kari hai. best moments were from Agra jab tumne namkeen alag tarah khana sikhaya, vedanth aur tune jo machaya tha bed pe regular intervals par aur agle din sab paper se saaf kia apan neğŸ˜... memories to kaafi hai jo likhne baithe to shayad khtm hi na ho ğŸ¤hopefully ye apni last party nahi hai aur apan milte rahenge.
author: Utkarsh  Sonkar

text: Mai pehli baar tujhe PE hi me mila tha...fir to 2nd yaer se labs aur tere hall pe aana aur bhagwan ki baatein karna exams se pehle tak...epic tha bhaiğŸ˜. Labs ke baad MT par casually milne aur cigs fooke se lekar kahi na kahi apan mil hi jaate the...par best memory apni labs ki hai jaha par apna launde logo ka aatank tha...bc kisi se campus me darna to bhul hi gaye the...milte rahenge zada door nahi hai apan(kanpur/ce buddies)âœŒï¸ğŸ¤

text:
Hum kaise mile ye raaz shayad na tujhe pata chala aur naa hi mujhe...best memory apni shayad RM me bakchodi kaatne se lekar har exam me laptop ki ladaki tak(endless) thi aur jo Kathi roll ki bakchodi thi bc andar se mai bhi khub hass raha tha...kabhi nahi lagta tha tum itna macha doge placement me ğŸ¤ , most importantly tum jitna bhi dank hone ka try karle par andar se ekdum humble banda hai tu... right from helping others to not giving a fuck jab apni marr rahi ho...ye maine tujhse seekha hai.

Jitne bhi kaand kie apan ne...RM ki suicide ki story se lekar mere hath ke stitches katwane tak jab Tera interview tha...sab yaad hai aur sath dene ke liye dhanyawad bro. Apne CE ke laundo se yaari ka shrey sirf vipul hai...aur poori lab ye janti thi kitne mc hai hum log ..right from bribing TA ki quizzes me number dedo (govind ki call) to Sir , maine iska assignment chapa hai par number kyu alag hai hum dono keğŸ˜...memories to endless hai apni...aise hi bane rehna aur unchaiyan choote rehnaâ¤ï¸... apan to milte rahenge aur "bhatere" party bachi hai abhi(you know what I mean)
author: Utkarsh  Sonkar
